=Description=

"Self-Aware Systems is a think tank working to build wisdom into emerging technologies to create a positive future. Wisdom consists of both intelligence and values, and new insights are required along both dimensions. We are developing a powerful new kind of artificial intelligence that combines logic with learning. We are also using recent advances in positive psychology, economics, evolutionary biology and moral philosophy to create a science of systems that support human values. By building both aspects into our technologies and institutions, we aim to contribute to the flourishing of the best of humanity."
(http://selfawaresystems.com/)

